==Hungarian==
===Noun===
'''csillag'''
# a luminous [[celestial]] body; [[star]]
#: ''A Szíriusz a legfényesebb '''csillag''' az égen.'' (Sirius is the brightest star on the sky)
# star-shaped [[symbol]]; [[asterisk]]
#: ''Hol van a '''csillag''' a billentyűzeten?'' (Where is the asterisk on the keyboard?)
# a person or thing held as a positive example
#: ''Ő a városunk '''csillaga'''.'' (She's our city's pride.)
# (vernacular) [[luck]]
#: ''Alkonyulóban van a '''csillaga'''.'' (He's getting unlucky)
# (informal) a person (sometimes animal) in a [[familiar]] relationship; [[girlfriend]] / [[boyfriend]] / [[child]] Used only in possessive case ''csillagom''.
#: ''Gyere ide, '''csillagom'''!'' (Come here my dear.)

